messages.content: Hi! How can I help you today?

Hello! I recently moved to a new house on Elm Avenue in Houston, and I have a couple of things I need help with. I ordered a luggage set that was sent to my new address, but I realized I have another order that was sent to my old address on the same street. I want to change the delivery address of that wrong order to my new home. Also, I want to update my user default address to the new home as well. I prefer not to disclose my address details, but you should be able to look it up in my orders. Additionally, I want to exchange a tablet I ordered for the cheapest one available due to moving costs. Can you assist me with these requests?
